{"tid":1978864,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"鐵證如山 雞丁係藍營 雞丁係建制 無撚屌錯","createTime":"2020-04-19T04:31:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-20T12:53:22.000Z","uid":286473,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6d72c93a1ff99a425252b880eba39b9f98691ffa","tid":1978864,"uid":286473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T04:31:19.000Z","msg":"由前財爺高官為合作份子<br />\n係為建制派維穩<br />\n連同前財爺的早前聯田北俊去做防疫街站<br />\n呢個雞丁極有可能為選舉時候<br />\n幫佢地作為主攻港島中年中產藍屍的吉祥物<br />\n你地知啦 d 40-60最好中意小朋友啦<br />\n又有一對老豆老母當個仔係搖錢樹<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">所以之前屌佢係藍絲要道歉位師兄<br />\n係無撚屌錯</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PJsGKEZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPJsGKEZ.jpg&h=6f7982b1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"55a060ab64329b9ff138cd82fe34479100d14d08","tid":1978864,"uid":286473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T04:33:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fff9b511abde2170872cf1d70be0fd939f36d7c6","tid":1978864,"uid":286473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T04:33:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"135b54bfa7d88f627e384bcbf8c110f31d6401cd","tid":1978864,"uid":286473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T04:33:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c82ba88c37ce4aab011cb2010ac556416b901fea","tid":1978864,"uid":286473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T04:33:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"67a7c9a9fb0ff9b93309afbe4e032b7f23ddc7ae","tid":1978864,"uid":286473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T04:34:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7c5186e1432cd3a170acf23937a371f65985e9db","tid":1978864,"uid":310700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T04:35:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clo